thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FmQRmW3.gif&h=632d4ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/oQRoBY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FoQRoBY.gif&h=a0f8959c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/zKPD8q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FzKPD8q.gif&h=4f30f486&s={SIZE}\" />...</blockquote><br />\n屍朗個d柒幾倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85d7880e2789eabfdb390f25264190f3575c325","tid":505901,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"單打我地美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b0e16dbcf1cf75ba48f39a8b5c24b11a757c9f","tid":505901,"uid":155902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg&h=1635bece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪近代體育史上最精彩既瑜亮之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n近代體育史嘅話<br />\n仲有費達拿同拿度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個好似鬥得仲癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無記錯好似0506年已經係世界排頭二, 而家大滿貫都好似佢地兩個拎最多....<br />\n<br />\n不過中間祖高域又跑出過ge.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a31ad0fc4a5d356841fd819acd405c120f6b577","tid":505901,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg&h=1635bece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪近代體育史上最精彩既瑜亮之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n近代體育史嘅話<br />\n仲有費達拿同拿度</blockquote><br />\n一個屈沙地，一個屈草地<br />\n無可比性喎"},{"pid":"ee2bd0f5ded06188a0522e949907d91196c0860f","tid":505901,"uid":42252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:58:13.000Z","msg":"球會誇啦啦 國家爛茶渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420602284e05824d6d8d2909b1e7ab50bf740dfb","tid":505901,"uid":84834,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:02:11.000Z","msg":"拿 <br />\n講明先<br />\n真心覺得C朗好勁<br />\n佢係條命衰<br />\n衰在佢同呢個痴線佬同一個年代<br />\n<br />\n睇下呢兩條片就知有幾癲<br />\n（兩條都係一場波入面的精華，睇全季集錦無意思，個個都係球王）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/Isx8srxCgQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIsx8srxCgQQ&d=nL7egrjVVTLOIcUIcKoS8ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=417ce19a\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/Isx8srxCgQQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/u9EaP96QsAA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fu9EaP96QsAA&d=nL7egrjVVTLOIcUIcKoS8ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=15cb595b\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/u9EaP96QsAA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時真係唔係話C朗差<br />\n但足球真係要成場睇 <br />\n剩睇數據其實真係唔準<br />\n<br />\n呢兩場波美斯都唔係入十幾廿球個種<br />\n但你睇下佢次拎波<br />\n對對手造成的威脅有幾大<br />\n人地要花幾多人去阻止佢<br />\n就知有幾恐怖<br />\n比人感覺真係一個人屌打人地全隊<br />\n<br />\nC朗勁個陣係腳風好 入三四球<br />\n睇比數會覺得佢一個人帶領球隊贏波<br />\n但佢入波集中係反擊/遠射/死球<br />\n全部都係要成隊波造出黎<br />\n問心如果佢係一隊弱隊踢<br />\n究竟仲可唔可以有咁多射門機會？<br />\n<br />\n美斯勁係勁在<br />\n就算踢史篤城<br />\n都可以吸引3/4個人埋黎逼佢<br />\n一係佢就過撚哂你<br />\n一係佢就用創造出黎的空位交波比人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後就係對足球的理解<br />\nC朗個種其實係運動員的典範<br />\n將每種物理上的可能加到最高<br />\n無人會否認佢係出色的足球員<br />\n因為佢送到個波入網<br />\n但睇佢踢波<br />\n你係唔會對足球加深左理解<br />\n<br />\n相反睇美斯/小白/沙維/布斯基斯踢波<br />\n你真係會覺得佢地用緊個腦踢波<br />\n每一個動作都係有作用<br />\n唔會插完花 又回後<br />\n或者一味trial and error 式的浪射<br />\n<br />\n如果朗癲係你最估佢唔到的球員<br />\n美斯應該係集足球智慧同技術於一體的典範<br />\n你望住佢<br />\n明知佢過你 你連拉都拉唔住 鏟跌佢 又企返起身<br />\n明知佢會傳 你估佢冇咁準會傳到 佢又真係傳到<br />\n明知佢會射 封哂位 佢都可以射埋你大細<br />\n<br />\n科學家已經研究過<br />\n美斯大腦的運動反射神經係萬中無一<br />\n先可以係極短時間內做正確的決定同動作<br />\n<br />\n有人話<br />\n係巴塞勁  先令到美斯勁<br />\n<br />\n其實係岩岩相反<br />\n成套傳控足球的核心就係做突破缺口的美斯<br />\n沙維小白係好重要<br />\n但足球最終都係要得分<br />\n一咪傳控係贏唔到比賽（2014西班牙就係咁）<br />\n數據上都反映到（助攻美斯最多的唔係沙維小白，反而係後上側擊的丹尼爾）<br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話好鍾意睇充滿力量 速度的足球<br />\n但從古到今<br />\n最為後人所讚頌的<br />\n都係有足球智慧的球員<br />\n因為體能會隨狀態而消逝<br />\n唯獨技術同智慧先係歷久不衰"},{"pid":"dd614b1c725c5005d0965da50ae3e988a8345685","tid":505901,"uid":46507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/21/233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F21%2F233134_a12d7c3d57d401afb1e4dfced2fbf9f4.jpg&h=1635bece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係咪近代體育史上最精彩既瑜亮之爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n近代體育史嘅話<br />\n仲有費達拿同拿度</blockquote><br />\n依兩個有明顯勝負"}]}